    <h3>Des nombres cardinaux aux ordinaux</h3>

    <p>Les cartes ci-dessus montrent les ordinaux (premier, deuxième...), pas les cardinaux (un, deux...). En arabe, les ordinaux de 3 à 10 se forment à partir de la racine du cardinal en suivant le schème فَاعِل (fāʻil). On prend les trois lettres de la racine et on les insère dans le moule فَاعِل. Pour le féminin, on ajoute ة : فَاعِلَة (fāʻila).</p>

    <div class="conj-table-wrapper">
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>#</th>
            <th>Cardinal</th>
            <th>Racine</th>
            <th class="ar">Ordinal ♂</th>
            <th class="ar">Ordinal ♀</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="num-col">1</td>
            <td class="verb-ar">وَاحِد</td>
            <td class="meaning-col">و ح د</td>
            <td class="verb-ar">وَاحِد</td>
            <td class="verb-ar">وَاحِدَة</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="num-col">2</td>
            <td class="verb-ar">اِثْنَان</td>
            <td class="meaning-col">ث ن ي</td>
            <td class="verb-ar">ثَانٍ</td>
            <td class="verb-ar">ثَانِيَة</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="pattern-row">
            <td class="num-col">3</td>
            <td class="verb-ar">ثَلَاثَة</td>
            <td class="meaning-col">ث ل ث</td>
            <td class="verb-ar">ثَالِث</td>
            <td class="verb-ar">ثَالِثَة</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="pattern-row">
            <td class="num-col">4</td>
            <td class="verb-ar">أَرْبَعَة</td>
            <td class="meaning-col">ر ب ع</td>
            <td class="verb-ar">رَابِع</td>
            <td class="verb-ar">رَابِعَة</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="pattern-row">
            <td class="num-col">5</td>
            <td class="verb-ar">خَمْسَة</td>
            <td class="meaning-col">خ م س</td>
            <td class="verb-ar">خَامِس</td>
            <td class="verb-ar">خَامِسَة</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="pattern-row">
            <td class="num-col">6</td>
            <td class="verb-ar">سِتَّة</td>
            <td class="meaning-col">س د س</td>
            <td class="verb-ar">سَادِس</td>
